We are introducing a new status called "Awaiting Review." This status will allow RCM Leads and delegates ("2LOD") to challenge the decision made by the LOB Head ("1LOD") when no changes are specified. 

Additionally, we will include the following fields: 
- Reviewer Decision 
- Review Comments 
- Reviewer 
- Review Date 

The reviewer ("2LOD") can make one of the following decisions:
- No: Confirm no change
- Yes: Regulatory Changes
- Yes: External Events 
- Yes: Internal Changes / Changes to Quality of Control

RCM Leads and delegates can find items awaiting their decision on the dashboard titled "XYZ." From there, they can navigate to the relevant record to make their decision or input it in bulk.

To provide more time for entering decisions, annual decisions will now be generated 30 days prior to the due date instead of 23 days.
